eck for unallocated memory after creating an empty instance. There’s also a potential issue with the `DefaultAllocationManagerFactory` class, and I need to consider avoiding direct dependency to ensure tests pass smoothly.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_JLRMeKSaiQCt38GMSVPfDnCm|fc_0d822cf5ea0740010169f706640848819692925c945bdf1f3c", "name": "read", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/org.apache.arrow/arrow-memory-core/7.0.0/src/test/java/org_apache_arrow/arrow_memory_core/DefaultAllocationManagerOptionTest.java"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1247, "output": 790, "cacheRead": 30720, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 32757, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777796694336, "responseId": "resp_0d822cf5ea0740010169f70656ca44819682a5be02817dace1"}}
